id: hide_attempt
title: "Hiding"
background_prompt: "dense forest with massive ancient gnarled twisted oak tree, hidden safe spot among roots and foliage, protective shadows, secretive atmosphere"

dialogue:
  - narrator: "You hide behind a large oak tree."
  - narrator: "Through the leaves, you see shadowy figures passing by."
  - narrator: "After they leave, you carefully make your way through the forest."
  - narrator: "You eventually find the forest's exit."

